<p> In Week 2, we created an interest form where people could give us their emails to show their interest in playtesting. 
    We put this form on posters that we physically hung up around campus and we made a post on Instagram to furthe promote playtesting. 
    Every time someone filled out the form, it would populate into a spreadsheet. From there, we added them into the email group. 
</p>
