<p> In Week 3, we sent our first playtesting sign-up email to the 26 people who had joined our email alias so far. 
    The email included all information about the sessions that we could and a link to a Sign-Up Genius where people could sign up. 
    We also posted a second time on the Instagram to promote the Sign-Up Genius 
</p>
