<h3 id="continuing" class="font-bold text-lg mt-6 mb-2">Continuing the Efforts</h3>
<p> Throughout the next few weeks, we would continue to add people to our email alias daily. 
    Any time someone was added, they received information about playtesting sessions along with the sign-up sheet. 
    On the Monday of every week, we would re-send the sign-up link to the entire email alias to remind people that they could sign-up for the coming weeks.
    We also continued to post about twice a week on Instagram to keep ourselves circulating on peoples' feeds.
</p>

