<h2 id="results" class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2 mt-6">The Results</h2>
<p> We had people filling out our interest form almost daily until Week 6 where it slowed down to every other day or so. 
    We also consistently saw playtesting sessions fill up about a week before they were scheduled to take place. 
    By the time we closed the interst form, we had 58 people on our emailing list. 
    Below is our Instagram analytics at the end of our 8 weeks of production.
</p>

