    <h3 id="learned1" class="font-semibold">Lesson 1: Market Early</h3>
        <p class="ml-8"> We started preparing our marketing when we started the project. We had posters up two weeks before we needed playtesters. We had full playtesting session sign-ups every week.</p>
    <h3 id="learned2" class="font-semibold mt-4">Lesson 2: Consistency</h3>
        <p class="ml-8">As we continued to post on Instagram, we continued to to see interactions with our posts.</p>
